2::0::Crown of the Barbarians~[az4v]
2::0::------------------------------
2::0::You discover a dull wrought-iron crown, crudely fashioned.  When
2::0::you place it upon your head, you sense the presence of several
2::0::bands of barbarians nearby.  You find these units will respond to
2::0::your mental control, and you can issue the following commands to
2::0::your barbarian units:
2::0::
2::0::   ADMIT, ATTACK, BANNER, BEHIND, CONTACT, DEFAULT, DEFEND, DROP,
2::0::   EXECUTE, FLAG, GIVE, HOSTILE, MOVE, NAME, NEUTRAL, PILLAGE,
2::0::   PROMOTE, RAZE, SEEK, STACK, STOP, TAKE, TERRORIZE, UNSTACK, WAIT
