2::0::You discover an ancient, tattered banner, bearing a crude symbol.
2::0::Upon raising the banner, you sense the presence of several bands of
2::0::skeletons nearby.  You find these units will respond to your mental
2::0::control, and you can issue the following commands to your skeleton
2::0::units:
2::0::
2::0::   ADMIT, ATTACK, BANNER, BEHIND, CONTACT, DEFAULT, DEFEND, DROP,
2::0::   EXECUTE, FLAG, GIVE, HOSTILE, MOVE, NAME, NEUTRAL, PILLAGE,
2::0::   PROMOTE, RAZE, SEEK, STACK, STOP, TAKE, TERRORIZE, UNSTACK, WAIT
